## 🎯 ÖNCELİKLENDİRİLMİŞ GELİŞTİRME PLANI

### Phase 1: KRİTİK GÜVENLİK (1-2 Hafta)
1. ✅ unwrap() → proper error handling
2. ✅ API key hardcoding → Vault entegrasyonu
3. ✅ SQL injection → parameterized queries
4. ✅ unsafe blokları → safe alternatifler

### Phase 2: KANAL ENTEGRASYONLARI (2-3 Hafta)
1. 🔴 Telegram (teloxide)
2. 🔴 Discord (serenity)
3. 🔴 Slack (slack-api)
4. 🔴 Email (lettre)
5. 🔴 Webhook

### Phase 3: SES & LLM (1-2 Hafta)
1. 🔴 Whisper STT (whisper-rs)
2. 🔴 Wake Word (vosk)
3. 🔴 Local LLM (GPT4All/LLaMA.cpp)
4. 🟠 Streaming STT

### Phase 4: TEE & ZK (2-3 Hafta)
1. 🔴 AMD SEV-SNP attestation
2. 🔴 Intel TDX attestation
3. 🔴 Groth16 proof generation
4. 🟠 HSM integration

### Phase 5: OTONOM AGENT (2-3 Hafta)
1. 🔴 Screen capture (x11rb)
2. 🔴 OCR (Tesseract)
3. 🔴 Mouse/Keyboard (enigo)
4. 🟠 UI Detection ML

### Phase 6: ENTERPRISE (1-2 Hafta)
1. 🟠 OAuth2 PKCE
2. 🟠 JWT validation
3. 🟠 RBAC detaylandırma
4. 🟠 Multi-tenancy

### Phase 7: TEST & BENCHMARK (1 Hafta)
1. 🔴 Benchmark implementations
2. 🔴 Integration tests
3. 🔴 Performance tests
4. 🟡 API documentation

